name: Fabled Fortress
blurb: Fabled Fortress is a hybrid strategy game about building, managing, and defending the kingdom of your dreams against ruthless invaders.

rewards.reward: LINUX TIER - We have not yet committed to a Linux release but with enough backers we can justify it. We have made this special tier just for the Linux community. \r\nIf released on Linux you will also get exclusive access to the game's BETA, access to the Orc Stronghold (provides access to premium Orc Quests), AND receive a copy of the final game. Are you ready to unleash your inner Orc? \r\nFor any dollar amount that you back under the LINUX TIER that is the amount of a higher tier you will receive all of the corresponding rewards. (Example: Back $50 under the Linux Tier and receive all rewards in the $50 tier). Please add $10 USD for international shipping.

GOBLIN TIER - \r\n\r\nGet exclusive access to the game's BETA, access to the Orc Stronghold (provides access to premium Orc Quests), AND receive a copy of the final game.  Are you ready to unleash your inner Orc?

ELVEN ARCHER TIER - Get the Ancestors Pack (custom Town Shield, unique Town Center, and in-game Gryphon statue), access to the Elven Palace (provides access to premium Elven Quests), and all previous tiers.  Become a legend in the world of Fabled Fortress as a founding Ancestor AND unlock the Elven forces.

SKELLINGTON TIER - Get a copy of the Fabled Fortress Digital Artbook, a copy of the complete Digital Soundtrack, and access to the Demon Fortress (which provides access to premium Undead Quests), Fabled Fortress Cubicature Set #1, appear in the game credits as a peasant plus all previous tiers!  Immerse yourself in the sights and sounds of Fabled Fortress AND summon the infection of the Undead!

SORCERER TIER - Get a Fabled Fortress T-Shirt, a set of 6 Spell Card tiles, Fabled Fortress Cubicature Set #2 and all previous tiers.  Take Fabled Fortress wherever you go! Note: Please add $10 USD for international shipping.

ROYAL GUARD TIER - Receive an exclusive set of Fabled Fortress posters, access to the fine Orange games private forum, Fabled Fortress Cubicature Set #3 and all previous tiers.  Be a member of our Royal Guard! Note: Please add $10 USD for international shipping.

KNIGHT TIER - Design a custom Spell, receive the rare Mounted Knight and Fabled Fortress Cubicature Set #4 plus receive all previous tiers.  The other kingdoms won't even see you coming! Price includes international shipping.

PALADIN TIER - Get the exclusive Fabled Founders Castle, receive an exclusive in-game statue that you design, the full set of Fabled Fortress Cubicatures and all previous rewards. Show the other kingdoms why you rule! Price includes international shipping..

GRYPHON TIER - Become an in-game character, receive an original portrait of your character signed by our lead graphic artist, receive an in-game statue of your character, plus all previous rewards. How cool is that!? Price includes international shipping.
